pick up a bottle from the bin
move to the toilet behind you
put the bottle on the bin
move to the bin to the left of the door
pick up a bottle from the bin
move to the toilet behind you
put the bottle on the bin
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles on the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the brown trash can on the floor next to the bathroom door.
Pick up the purple and white spray bottle out of the trash can.
Turn around and go to the front of the toilet.
Place the spray cleaner on the top of the toilet tank on the left of the toilet paper.
Turn around and go back to the brown trash can on the floor.
Pick up the remaining purple and white spray bottle out of the trash can.
Turn around and go back to the toilet.
Place the second spray bottle on the right of the first bottle and next to the toilet paper.
anns.task_desc: Move the spray cleaners to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn right and face the red trash can in front of you.
Take out the spray bottle in the red trash can in front of you.
Turn around and face the toilet in front of you.
Place the spray bottle on the toilet in front of you.
Turn around and face the red trash can in front of you.
Take the spray bottle from the red trash can in front of you.
Turn around and face the toilet in front of you.
Place the spray bottle on the toilet in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles on top of the toilet.
